video_title: You learn a lot when parenting your children. #parenting #jayshetty #melindagates
transcript:
you learn a lot when you're parenting
your children like you may think oh I'm
a patient person but you have no idea
what patience is until you have children
and until you really are trying to pass
your values on you have to really kind
of sit with okay what are my values I
thought I knew them but am I living them
so that I can pass them on
